        "body": "Changes\r\n\r\nAdded a new test case in packages/turbo-utils/tests/getTurboConfigs.test.ts to verify that getTurboConfigs correctly throws an error when both turbo.json and turbo.jsonc exist in the same directory.\r\n\r\nRemoved an outdated TODO comment in packages/turbo-utils/src/getTurboConfigs.ts, as the logic for detecting conflicting configuration files is already implemented.\r\n\r\nWhy\r\n\r\nAlthough the codebase already handled the case where both config files are present, there was no dedicated test to ensure this behavior remains stable over time.\r\nAdditionally, a stale TODO comment implied the behavior was a known issue, which was inaccurate. The comment has been removed to reflect the current, correct implementation.\r\n\r\nVerification\r\n\r\nRan pnpm --filter @turbo/utils test and confirmed that all tests passed successfully, including the newly added test case.",
